text: Murrayville is an unincorporated community in Hall County, Georgia, United States. The community is located along Georgia State Route 60, north-northwest of Gainesville. Murrayville has a post office with ZIP code 30564. The community was named after Patrick J. Murray, a local merchant. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Hall County, Georgia Category:Unincorporated communities in Georgia (U.S. state)
title: Murrayville, Georgia
